    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Miller International Field, Mc allen, Jexas",
      "FW-520\nMILLER INTERNATIONAL FIELD, McAllen, Texas\noffers the finest, modern facilities for the commercial\nairline passenger as well as for private and corporate\npilots. As an official United States Port of Entry,\nprovides custom services to a large traffic of private\naircraft flying to and from Old Mexico.\nAerial Color by Frank B. Whaley\nPub. by FRANK WHALEY POST CARDS - 705 N. 10th - McAllen, Texas\nPLACE\nSTAMP\nHERE\nPost Card\n67085-8\ndp DEXTER PRESS, INC\nWEST NYACK, NEW YORK\n2015.116.2079"
    ],
